abstract: >-
  Open-source companion artifact suite for the paper "A Practical Cybersecurity
  Framework for Legacy Medical Devices". Five integrated practitioner-oriented
  frameworks for healthcare delivery organisations and medical device
  manufacturers operating under legacy device constraints, comprising:
  the Medical Device Risk Score (MDRS) reference calculator with
  irreversibility-driven tier floor; STRIDE-HC threat-modelling templates
  for the dual network/physical attack surface; Control Justification Record
  templates aligned to ISO 14971, AAMI TIR57, and FDA 524B; a Dockerised
  empirical test harness; and a software reference design for the inline
  service-port multi-factor authentication shim (Pattern C).
